high_descs: Turn to the left and walk straight back. Find the fridge on the right.
Open the fridge and take out a tomato. Shut the door.
Carry the tomato and turn left then left again to find the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the tomato inside. Shut the door and then open the door and take out the tomato. Shut the door.
Carry the tomato and turn around to the island.
Place the tomato on the island, towards the front center.
anns.task_desc: Heat a tomato and place it on the counter.

high_descs: Take a step forward then turn left and walk to the fridge that will be on your right turning right to face it once you get to it.
Open the fridge and grab the tomato that you see in there then close the door.
Turn left and walk to the counter then turn left and walk to the microwave.
Cook the tomato in the microwave then take it back out and close the door.
Turn left and walk until your even with the bread on the counter then turn left when you are and take a step forward.
Put the tomato on the edge of the counter under the bread.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved tomato on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the front of the refrigerator.
Pick up the red tomato on the second shelf in the refrigerator.
Turn left and go around the island to the microwave above the dishwasher.
Heat the tomato in the microwave and take it out.
Turn around and go to the right side of the island with the bread on top.
Place the tomato on the island in front of the bread.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato on the island.
